‘’HUSTLE’’ the movie where ‘’The smart gets conned, the conned get smarter’’. The official trailer for Marc Adebesin‘s upcoming movie, “Hustle” is here to thrill you ahead of its nationwide cinematic release on the 9th of July. <img loading="lazy" src="https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/image008-1024x589.jpg" alt="" width="740" height="426" srcset="https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/image008-1024x589.jpg 1024w, https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/image008-300x173.jpg 300w, https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/image008-1536x884.jpg 1536w, https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/image008-2048x1178.jpg 2048w" sizes="(max-width: 740px) 100vw, 740px"> HUSTLE Official thriller: <img src="https://i.ytimg.com/vi/6TQ4O540Mf0/hqdefault.jpg" alt="Hustle Official Trailer | NANCY ISIME | GABRIEL AFOLAYAN | JIM IYKE | BIMBO ADEMOYE | FEMI BRANCH"> “HUSTLE’’ tells the tale of Chichi and her friend “with benefits”, Baba Gee, set out to play games on the affluent men of the society, and in a no strings attached relationship. Chichi ends up falling for her potential victim who just arrived after a few years in Cameroon. Unknown to her, this victim was an old dog in the game and willing to teach her a thing or two about it. A cunning twist awaits chichi as she digs deeper to find out more about her new victim’s past. Dramas of contemporary Africa has been described as an unpredictable kaleidoscope, thriller, and suspense, carefully built up to a climactic epic finale. As a hustler Surviving in Lagos is the name of the game. <img loading="lazy" src="https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/image007-1024x589.jpg" alt="" width="740" height="426" srcset="https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/image007-1024x589.jpg 1024w, https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/image007-300x173.jpg 300w, https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/image007-1536x884.jpg 1536w, https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/image007-2048x1178.jpg 2048w" sizes="(max-width: 740px) 100vw, 740px"> “Hustle” features an amazing casts that includes Woli Arole, Bolaji Ogunmola, Femi Branch, Princess Brun Njua, Chinonso Ukah, Jeffrey Epule and Kelechi Ayinkude. <img loading="lazy" src="https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/image006-1024x589.jpg" alt="" width="740" height="426" srcset="https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/image006-1024x589.jpg 1024w, https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/image006-300x173.jpg 300w, https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/image006-1536x884.jpg 1536w, https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/image006-2048x1178.jpg 2048w" sizes="(max-width: 740px) 100vw, 740px"> The movie is produced by Marc Adebesin and Omowunmi Olunloyo who also serve as executive producers alongside Roseline Fonkwa Mound Jongui, Femi Oladiran and Ayo Ajayi. <img loading="lazy" src="https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/image005-1024x589.jpg" alt="" width="740" height="426" srcset="https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/image005-1024x589.jpg 1024w, https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/image005-300x173.jpg 300w, https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/image005-1536x884.jpg 1536w, https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/image005-2048x1178.jpg 2048w" sizes="(max-width: 740px) 100vw, 740px"> There would be a meet and greet session with all the cast within the first week of release at various cinemas across the nation. Interview with Marc Adebesin the Director: <img src="https://i.ytimg.com/vi/q3iD2XB7FFc/hqdefault.jpg" alt="Film producer Marc Adebesin on The WAY Show Weekly"> https://www.instagram.com/omowunmi_toks https://www.instagram.com/peacockomowunmi https://www.facebook.com/PeacockOmowunmi  <img loading="lazy" src="https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Hustle-Movie-Gabriel-Afolayan-Character-Poster-@mayodesigns_-724x1024.jpg" alt="" width="724" height="1024" srcset="https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Hustle-Movie-Gabriel-Afolayan-Character-Poster-@mayodesigns_-724x1024.jpg 724w, https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Hustle-Movie-Gabriel-Afolayan-Character-Poster-@mayodesigns_-212x300.jpg 212w, https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Hustle-Movie-Gabriel-Afolayan-Character-Poster-@mayodesigns_-1086x1536.jpg 1086w, https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Hustle-Movie-Gabriel-Afolayan-Character-Poster-@mayodesigns_-1448x2048.jpg 1448w, https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Hustle-Movie-Gabriel-Afolayan-Character-Poster-@mayodesigns_-scaled.jpg 1810w" sizes="(max-width: 724px) 100vw, 724px"><img loading="lazy" src="https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Hustle-Movie-Femi-Branch-Character-Poster-@mayodesigns_-724x1024.jpg" alt="" width="724" height="1024" srcset="https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Hustle-Movie-Femi-Branch-Character-Poster-@mayodesigns_-724x1024.jpg 724w, https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Hustle-Movie-Femi-Branch-Character-Poster-@mayodesigns_-212x300.jpg 212w, https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Hustle-Movie-Femi-Branch-Character-Poster-@mayodesigns_-1086x1536.jpg 1086w, https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Hustle-Movie-Femi-Branch-Character-Poster-@mayodesigns_-1448x2048.jpg 1448w, https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Hustle-Movie-Femi-Branch-Character-Poster-@mayodesigns_-scaled.jpg 1810w" sizes="(max-width: 724px) 100vw, 724px"><img loading="lazy" src="https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Hustle-Movie-Bolaji-Ogunmola-Character-Poster-@mayodesigns_-724x1024.jpg" alt="" width="724" height="1024" srcset="https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Hustle-Movie-Bolaji-Ogunmola-Character-Poster-@mayodesigns_-724x1024.jpg 724w, https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Hustle-Movie-Bolaji-Ogunmola-Character-Poster-@mayodesigns_-212x300.jpg 212w, https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Hustle-Movie-Bo